systemd-dissect, systemd-escape, systemd-hwdb, systemd-id128,
systemd-inhibit, systemd-machine-id-setup, systemd-mount, systemd-notify,
systemd-nspawn, systemd-path, systemd-repart, systemd-resolve (symlink to
resolvectl), systemd-run, systemd-socket-activate, systemd-stdio-bridge,
systemd-sysext, systemd-tmpfiles, systemd-tty-ask-password-agent,
